OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski has
OL,7,Fadmitted he was wrong to claim to be a
OL,8,FBritish Red Cross spokesperson.
OL,10,FA report by the Times revealed
OL,11,FPolanski made the claim in both 2020
OL,12,Fand 2022 while campaigning to be the
OL,13,Fparty's deputy leader.
OL,15,FIn information included on Polanski's
OL,16,Fformer websites and promotional pages,
OL,17,Fthe Green leader claimed to have acted
OL,18,Fas a spokesperson, something the
OL,19,FBritish Red Cross denied.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FSpeaking to BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,7,Fprogramme on Wednesday, Polanski said:
OL,8,F"I hosted various fundraisers for the
OL,9,FBritish Red Cross, and indeed, I would
OL,10,Fgo on stage and speak for them about
OL,11,Fthe amazing work they do tackling
OL,12,Fhumanitarian crises, on the climate
OL,13,Fcrisis, and indeed, for refugees all
OL,14,Faround the world.
OL,16,F"I used the wrong word, and I accept
OL,17,Fthat, but I would essentially take
OL,18,Fwords on stage with me and speak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,F"It's important, though, and I accept
OL,7,Fthis, that they don't support any
OL,8,Fpolitical party, and I've made sure
OL,9,Fthat's been taken down."
OL,11,FPolanski has, at various times, helped
OL,12,Frun fundraisers for the British Red
OL,13,FCross, but as a charity, the
OL,14,Forganisation must remain non-party
OL,15,Fpolitical.
OL,17,FWith just one day to go until the
OL,18,Flocal elections, the Green Party and
OL,19,Fits leader have faced increased
OL,20,Fscrutiny over their actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
