OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FFurther questions around Polanski's CV
OL,7,Fwere also raised by the Times report,
OL,8,Fwhich claimed Polanski was not a full
OL,9,Fmember of the National Council of
OL,10,FHypnotherapy while working as a
OL,11,Fhypnotherapist, despite claiming to be
OL,12,Fso to potential clients.
OL,14,FPolanski has previously faced
OL,15,Fcriticism over his time working in
OL,16,Fhypnotherapy for claiming to an
OL,17,Fundercover journalist he could
OL,18,Fincrease her breast size with
OL,19,Fhypnotherapy, something he has since
OL,20,Fapologised for and argued was taken
OL,21,Fout of context.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
