OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FCriticism has also been levelled at
OL,7,FPolanski in recent days over his
OL,8,Fresponse to the antisemitic attack
OL,9,Flast week in Golders Green on two
OL,10,FJewish men.
OL,12,FIn the wake of the attack, Polanski
OL,13,Fshared a post on social media
OL,14,Fcriticising how the police officers
OL,15,Fhandled the incident after footage
OL,16,Fshowed two officers repeatedly kicking
OL,17,Fthe suspect in the head.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FHis sharing of the post led to
OL,7,Fcriticism from the Met Police
OL,8,FCommissioner, Sir Mark Rowley, who
OL,9,Fwrote a letter to the Green leader
OL,10,Fpraising his officers and criticising
OL,11,FPolanski's sharing of the post.
OL,13,FPolanski apologised for sharing the
OL,14,Fpost in haste, offering to meet
OL,15,Fprivately with Rowley.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
