CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Polanski said:
OL,7,F"Two things can be true at the same
OL,8,Ftime: officers are incredibly brave
OL,9,Fwhen they run towards scenes of crimes
OL,10,Fthat most people, including myself,
OL,11,Fwill want to run away from.
OL,13,F"At the same time, I think it is
OL,14,Faccurate, and that I was also
OL,15,Ftraumatised by seeing someone
OL,16,Fhandcuffed and repeatedly kicked in
OL,17,Fthe head."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
