OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Green Party has also faced
OL,12,Fcriticism over the vetting of some of
OL,13,Fits candidates standing in this week's
OL,14,Flocal elections.
OL,16,FConfronted with a series of comments
OL,17,Fmade by his candidates, the Green
OL,18,Fleader said: "Those messages are all
OL,19,Funacceptable, and it's important to
OL,20,Fcondemn that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
