PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,F"The Green Party are an anti-racist
OL,7,Fparty, and it's important that we
OL,8,Fstick to our values."
OL,10,FHe said there would be a "standardised
OL,11,Fvetting process" in the future, with
OL,12,Fcompulsory training for candidates,
OL,13,F"to make it clear that antisemitism is
OL,14,Fcompletely unwelcome in the Green
OL,15,FParty, as it is in society".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,F"It is also important to say one case
OL,7,Fof antisemitism is one too many. This
OL,8,Fis a handful of cases, and actually,
OL,9,Fwe have over 4,500 candidates, the
OL,10,Fvast, vast majority of which are doing
OL,11,Famazing work in their communities
OL,12,Fright now."
OL,14,FOn Tuesday evening, the Labour Party
OL,15,Freleased a list of 25 Green Party
OL,16,Fcandidates it claimed had made
OL,17,Fproblematic comments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
