OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FSeveral of these had already been
OL,7,Fpublicised, including two Green
OL,8,Fcandidates for Lambeth council in
OL,9,Fsouth London, Sabine Mairey and Saiqa
OL,10,FAli, who were arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fstirring up racial hatred online.
OL,13,FPosts made by Ali on social media
OL,14,Fshowed she had posted an image of an
OL,15,Farmed man wearing a headband of the
OL,16,Fbanned Islamist group Hamas, along
OL,17,Fwith the slogan: "Resistance is
OL,18,Ffreedom."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
