OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FAnother image showed Mairey had shared
OL,7,Fa post with the message: "Ramming a
OL,8,Fsynagogue isn't antisemitism. It's
OL,9,Frevenge."
OL,11,FBoth have been suspended by the party,
OL,12,Fand a spokesperson added: "Where there
OL,13,Fare examples brought to our attention
OL,14,Fthat do not align with the values of
OL,15,Fthe Green party, we are looking into
OL,16,Fthem, and in some cases, candidates
OL,17,Fhave already been suspended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
