OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778087158
OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,FShe added: "Lots of people in the
OL,7,FGreen Party, you can see, are away
OL,8,Fwith the fairies, they are not serious
OL,9,Fat all. Zack Polanski was criticising
OL,10,Fthe police who were apprehending a man
OL,11,Fwho just tried to kill two people.
OL,12,FThat's not what a serious party leader
OL,13,Fdoes."
OL,15,FResponding to Polanski's words on
OL,16,FWednesday, Communities Secretary Steve
OL,17,FReed said: "Polanski is still refusing
OL,18,Fto sack candidates who have shared
OL,19,Fdisgusting antisemitic posts despite
OL,20,Fsaying he takes full responsibility
OL,21,Ffor them.
