OL,3,CZack Polanski admits he was wrong to
OL,4,Ccall himself a Red Cross spokesperson
OL,6,F"Following the horrific knife attack
OL,7,Fon two Jewish men in Golders Green he
OL,8,Fcontinues to show concern for the
OL,9,Fsuspected attacker. And his response
OL,10,Fto allegations that he lied about his
OL,11,Fpast job and qualifications shows he
OL,12,Fsimply can't be trusted."
